rows.label: qst703004_msg0001
rows.name:
You saved our lives!
Thank you!

rows.label: qst703004_msg0002
rows.name:
Did you find the Melosian Honey
that you sought?

rows.label: qst703004_msg0006
rows.name:
Melosian Honey's pretty valuable, and
this is the only place in Gula it can
be gathered.

rows.label: qst703004_msg0007
rows.name:
The special envoy insisted we needed
some to give to the Superbians...

rows.label: qst703004_msg0008
rows.name:
I'd also be interested in finding out
how delicious it is, but I value people's
safety over anything else.

rows.label: qst703004_msg0010
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]This youth seems far more capable
of leadership than Mr. Jarque...

rows.label: qst703004_msg0011
rows.name:
We risk another Skeeter
attack if we remain here.

rows.label: qst703004_msg0012
rows.name:
You're right...
Let's go back to the special envoy.
